title: The Warriors Are Officially Back
description:
In this edition of (debatable) After Dark, Pablo Torre, Dominque Foxworth and Israel Gutierrez debate if the Warriors feel like a juggernaut again and how Steph will be viewed with another trip to the NBA Finals.
